HEADWORD: Unification
<hw>U`ni*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Unify</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of unifying, or the state of being
unified.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Unification</qex> with God was the final aim of the
Neoplatonicians.</q> <rj><qau>Fleming.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unifier</ent>⟦br⟧
